ally: the title. The idea of changing it does not appeal to my husband very much. But he understands your problem. Do you have some title in mind that would make PLAYBOY feel happier?)*

Please note the new address at which we shall stay for several weeks. Letters mailed to Montreux will be forwarded and will also reach us.

With best wishes,





Sincerely,

(Mrs. Vladimir Nabokov)





TO: BARBARA EPSTEIN

CC, 1 p.





St. Moritz, July 8, 1965

Suvretta House

